{"tid":535954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV男優與AV女優交往　破壞業界規則遭恐嚇","createTime":"2018-01-21T11:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T12:00:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1b21ebb3a3a3acac82ce36f0212f39a832edd226","tid":535954,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"AV男優跟AV女優私下交往，遭到日本暴走族集團「關東聯合」前幹部，以違反業界規則為由，恐嚇200萬日圓(約53萬新台幣)，被警方以恐嚇未遂逮捕。<br />\n據《TBS》報導，遭到逮捕的3人，分別是前AV導演松嶋Cross(本名)松嶋重、脫衣舞廳的老闆松本和彦、佐久間孝文。這3人涉嫌在前年2月份時，於東京「淺草ROCK座」的接待室，對38歲的AV男優進行恐嚇200萬日圓，起因為，該位AV男友的後輩，跟AV女優交往，違反了業界的規則。被逮後松嶋重抱持沉默沒有發言，松本和彦則否認，「我沒有威脅」。<br />\n引退的AV「女優」大島薰，在《推特》發文指出，AV男優被威脅根本是家常便飯。至於幫後輩出面的AV男優是誰？日本網友根據年齡猜測，有可能是38歲的森林原人、清水健。<br />\n<br />\n拍拖唔俾？"},{"pid":"76edbd0fd83870296537bf9537d1b44802768dcb","tid":535954,"uid":60366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"大島薰算係女優黎乜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5704869289fde00b65e77c72b9a6ee2a27235d66","tid":535954,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"日本av女優地位好高架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78b847d671afc73d3525261330a29a4fe92a38d","tid":535954,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"有鳩的妖魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94da872644a557be2c3fd1641b60d3c14316cfd3","tid":535954,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"38歲的AV男優<br />\n<br />\n可能係清水健或森林原人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733ce57d0ba20fce77db3d9865cd832b4610b5fb","tid":535954,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"清水健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkg